    {
      "parameters": {
        "chatId": "8770824903",
        "text": "=🎵 *FF Social - Music needed!*\n\nA post is ready but needs music added before it goes live.\n\n*Caption:* {{ $json.caption }}\n*Scheduled:* {{ $json.scheduled_at }}\n*Post ID:* `{{ $json.id }}`\n\n1. Open Instagram\n2. Post it with music added\n3. Update status to `posted` in the sheet",
